(100003, 0, 'Liquid Handling', 20002, 1, 'We offer a varied range of high quality and durable pipette and pipette tips for maximal accuracy and precision. The universal design offer a level of compatibility and functionalities for end user convenience. The pipettes and pipette tips are designed taking into consideration every user\'s need and precised mode of application. The processing and packaging provide highest level of liquid handling performance.', 'Liquid Handling', 'Liquid-Handling', 'Labware | Liquid Handling | Lab Equipment', 'We offer a varied range of high quality and durable pipette and pipette tips for maximal accuracy and precision. The universal design offer a level of compatibility and functionalities for end user convenience. The pipettes and pipette tips are designed taking into consideration every user\'s need and precised mode of application. The processing and packaging provide highest level of liquid handling performance.', 'Liquid Handling', 'Liquid Handling', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling', NULL),
(100004, 0, 'Centrifuge Consumables', 20002, 1, 'We offer a broad range of centrifugeware, employed in variety of centrifugation method in laboratories. These products acts as consumables item in the laboratory having unique features that reveal their fine quality.  The moulding of these products is attained from pure material that yield low extractability and leaching on being used.', 'Centrifuge Consumables', 'Centrifuge-Consumables', 'Labware | Centrifuge Consumables | Lab Equipment', 'We offer a broad range of centrifugeware, employed in variety of centrifugation method in laboratories. These products acts as consumables item in the laboratory having unique features that reveal their fine quality.  The moulding of these products is attained from pure material that yield low extractability and leaching on being used.', 'Centrifuge Consumables', 'Centrifuge Consumables', NULL, 'Labware/Centrifuge-Consumables', NULL),
(100005, 0, 'Cell Culture Products', 20002, 1, 'We offer wide range of cell culture products for reliability and protection against contamination. A complete range of cell culture media is included with treated and no -treated surfaces as per the desired user application. All the consumables are treated with surface modifications for various use. High quality and best value products are included with a range of packing methods for transportation convenience.', 'Cell Culture Products', 'Cell-Culture-Products', 'Labware | Cell Culture Products | Lab Equipment', 'We offer wide range of cell culture products for reliability and protection against contamination. A complete range of cell culture media is included with treated and no -treated surfaces as per the desired user application. All the consumables are treated with surface modifications for various use. High quality and best value products are included with a range of packing methods for transportation convenience.', 'Cell Culture Products', 'Cell Culture Products', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products', NULL),
(100006, 0, 'CryoTubes', 100001, 2, 'Our Cryo Vials facilitate sterilized technique exceptionally devised for cryogenic storage and transport of biological specimens in extreme temperatures. Tubes can be effortlessly recognized using the white marking area and can be color coded with cap inserts, available separately.', 'CryoTubes', 'CryoTubes', 'Laboratory Plasticware | CryoTubes | Lab Equipment', 'Our Cryo Vials facilitate sterilized technique exceptionally devised for cryogenic storage and transport of biological specimens in extreme temperatures. Tubes can be effortlessly recognized using the white marking area and can be color coded with cap inserts, available separately.', 'CryoTubes', 'CryoTubes', NULL, 'Labware/Laboratory-Plasticware/CryoTubes', NULL),
(100007, 0, 'PCR Tubes', 100001, 2, 'PCR Tube features ultra-thin walls for excellent heat transfer and unique cap design, resulting in virtually no sample evaporation. Its bottom is conical and round shaped for maximum sample recovery. Designed for oil-free operation, the conical shape provides better contact under heated thermal cycling while eliminating condensation.', 'PCR Tubes', 'PCR-Tubes', 'Laboratory Plasticware | PCR Tubes | Lab Equipment', 'PCR Tube features ultra-thin walls for excellent heat transfer and unique cap design, resulting in virtually no sample evaporation. Its bottom is conical and round shaped for maximum sample recovery. Designed for oil-free operation, the conical shape provides better contact under heated thermal cycling while eliminating condensation.', 'PCR Tubes', 'PCR Tubes', NULL, 'Labware/Laboratory-Plasticware/PCR-Tubes', NULL),
(100008, 0, 'PCR 96 Well Plate', 100001, 2, 'PCR 96 well plate are thin-walled tubes with uninterrupted allowance of heat transfer from the block into the sample. Made of highest grade virgin polypropylene specifically selected for minimal binding of DNA, RNA, and enzymes with maximum recovery and also in small volumes. Raised well rims provide effective sealing and reduce the risk of cross-contamination.', 'PCR 96 Well Plate', 'PCR-96-Well-Plate', 'Laboratory Plasticware | PCR 96 Well Plate | Lab Equipment', 'PCR 96 well plate are thin-walled tubes with uninterrupted allowance of heat transfer from the block into the sample. Made of highest grade virgin polypropylene specifically selected for minimal binding of DNA, RNA, and enzymes with maximum recovery and also in small volumes. Raised well rims provide effective sealing and reduce the risk of cross-contamination.', 'PCR 96 Well Plate', 'PCR 96 Well Plate', NULL, 'Labware/Laboratory-Plasticware/PCR-96-Well-Plate', NULL),
(100009, 0, 'Cryovials Holder', 100001, 2, 'Cryovials holder with stability in temperature between -196 ÂºC to 121 ÂºC. It is autoclavable and chemically resistant to alcohols and mild organic solvents. A transparent cover with numerical grid allows easy individual sample identification.', 'Cryovials Holder', 'Cryovials-Holder', 'Laboratory Plasticware | Cryovials Holder | Lab Equipment', 'Cryovials holder with stability in temperature between -196 ÂºC to 121 ÂºC. It is autoclavable and chemically resistant to alcohols and mild organic solvents. A transparent cover with numerical grid allows easy individual sample identification.', 'Cryovials Holder', 'Cryovials Holder', NULL, 'Labware/Laboratory-Plasticware/Cryovials-Holder', NULL),
(100010, 0, 'Bottles', 100002, 2, 'Our PET bottles are leak-proof reagent bottles made from medical grade material with a sterilization level of 10-6. Available in varying range of sizes and capacities. Clear graduation provides a visual reference of sample volume. DNase, RNase and Pyrogen free, providing product integrity assurance.', 'Bottles', 'Bottles', 'General Laboratory Products | Bottles | Lab Equipment', 'Our PET bottles are leak-proof reagent bottles made from medical grade material with a sterilization level of 10-6. Available in varying range of sizes and capacities. Clear graduation provides a visual reference of sample volume. DNase, RNase and Pyrogen free, providing product integrity assurance.', 'Bottles', 'Bottles', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Bottles', NULL),
(100011, 0, 'Petri Dish', 100002, 2, 'Petri dish are pre sterilized dishes made up of Polystyrene with numeric codes for easy user identification. The inner surface is molded with vent for air exchange. Equipped with serrated ring for easy handling. DNase, RNase and Pyrogen free, providing product integrity assurance.', 'Petri Dish', 'Petri-Dish', 'General Laboratory Products | Petri Dish | Lab Equipment', 'Petri dish are pre sterilized dishes made up of Polystyrene with numeric codes for easy user identification. The inner surface is molded with vent for air exchange. Equipped with serrated ring for easy handling. DNase, RNase and Pyrogen free, providing product integrity assurance.', 'Petri Dish', 'Petri Dish', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Petri-Dish', NULL),
(100012, 0, 'Test Tube', 100002, 2, 'Test tube are chemically resistant plastic tubes with a maximum attainable RCF of 5000 x g without any crack or leakage. Available with flexibility of customized labels for end user convenience. Made from Polypropylene and Polystyrene for adaptation to most common lab chemicals.', 'Test Tube', 'Test-Tube', 'General Laboratory Products | Test Tube | Lab Equipment', 'Test tube are chemically resistant plastic tubes with a maximum attainable RCF of 5000 x g without any crack or leakage. Available with flexibility of customized labels for end user convenience. Made from Polypropylene and Polystyrene for adaptation to most common lab chemicals.', 'Test Tube', 'Test Tube', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Test-Tube', NULL),
(100013, 0, 'Beaker', 100002, 2, 'Beakers are resilient to most generally used laboratory reagents, including a variety of strong acids, bases, and organic solvents. Polypropylene beakers are the foremost choice for scientific applications. All beakers are transparent for clear content visibility and graduated for easily estimating volumes.', 'Beaker', 'Beaker', 'General Laboratory Products | Beaker | Lab Equipment', 'Beakers are resilient to most generally used laboratory reagents, including a variety of strong acids, bases, and organic solvents. Polypropylene beakers are the foremost choice for scientific applications. All beakers are transparent for clear content visibility and graduated for easily estimating volumes.', 'Beaker', 'Beaker', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Beaker', NULL),
(100014, 0, 'Measuring Cylinder', 100002, 2, 'Measuring Cylinder features permanently-molded, prominent graduations that is visible even after repetitive autoclaving. Large round bottom provides excellent stability on the bench top.  Autoclavable at 121 Â°C.', 'Measuring Cylinder', 'Measuring-Cylinder', 'General Laboratory Products | Measuring Cylinder | Lab Equipment', 'Measuring Cylinder features permanently-molded, prominent graduations that is visible even after repetitive autoclaving. Large round bottom provides excellent stability on the bench top.  Autoclavable at 121 Â°C.', 'Measuring Cylinder', 'Measuring Cylinder', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Measuring-Cylinder', NULL),
(100015, 0, 'Volumetric Flask', 100002, 2, 'Volumetric Flasks with plastic plug in cap provides enhanced lab convenience, wide range of selection and accurate in volume measurement. Resilient and exclusive in strength. The graduation line is sharp and enduring, large block letters make the label easy to read.', 'Volumetric Flask', 'Volumetric-Flask', 'General Laboratory Products | Volumetric Flask | Lab Equipment', 'Volumetric Flasks with plastic plug in cap provides enhanced lab convenience, wide range of selection and accurate in volume measurement. Resilient and exclusive in strength. The graduation line is sharp and enduring, large block letters make the label easy to read.', 'Volumetric Flask', 'Volumetric Flask', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Volumetric-Flask', NULL),
(100016, 0, 'Test Tube Rack', 100002, 2, 'Test tube racks are designed to hold a wide range of test tube sizes. Durable and convenient racks are molded in a single, continuous piece so no assemblage is required. It has excellent chemical resistance and refrain from corrosion, chipping and peeling.', 'Test Tube Rack', 'Test-Tube-Rack', 'General Laboratory Products | Test Tube Rack | Lab Equipment', 'Test tube racks are designed to hold a wide range of test tube sizes. Durable and convenient racks are molded in a single, continuous piece so no assemblage is required. It has excellent chemical resistance and refrain from corrosion, chipping and peeling.', 'Test Tube Rack', 'Test Tube Rack', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Test-Tube-Rack', NULL),
(100017, 0, 'Pipette Tips', 100003, 2, 'Our pipette tips are autoclavable pre-sterilized with defined color codes for easy user identification. Long and short type variation with a micro-point design provides excellent reproducibility and accuracy. Adaptable to single and multi-channel pipette for high level precision.', 'Pipette Tips', 'Pipette-Tips', 'Liquid Handling | Pipette Tips | Lab Equipment', 'Our pipette tips are autoclavable pre-sterilized with defined color codes for easy user identification. Long and short type variation with a micro-point design provides excellent reproducibility and accuracy. Adaptable to single and multi-channel pipette for high level precision.', 'Pipette Tips', 'Pipette Tips', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling/Pipette-Tips', NULL),
(100018, 0, 'Pipettes', 100003, 2, 'Our pipettes are designed for precise and instant fluid dispensing. Made of medical grade polystyrene, gamma irradiation sterilized. The precise, black, highly readable permanent graduations prevent ambiguity and guarantee precise reading and accurate dispensing. Negative graduations provide additional pipetting volume.', 'Pipettes', 'Pipettes', 'Liquid Handling | Pipettes | Lab Equipment', 'Our pipettes are designed for precise and instant fluid dispensing. Made of medical grade polystyrene, gamma irradiation sterilized. The precise, black, highly readable permanent graduations prevent ambiguity and guarantee precise reading and accurate dispensing. Negative graduations provide additional pipetting volume.', 'Pipettes', 'Pipettes', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling/Pipettes', NULL),
(100019, 0, 'Micropipettes', 100003, 2, 'We offer a comprehensive collection of micropipettes with levels of accuracy and precision designed for better and quick one handed operation, these are used to dispense measured volume of liquids with a rapid release valve for quick and easy dispensing. These are autoclavable and light to use with disposable pipette tips.', 'Micropipettes', 'Micropipettes', 'Liquid Handling | Micropipettes | Lab Equipment', 'We offer a comprehensive collection of micropipettes with levels of accuracy and precision designed for better and quick one handed operation, these are used to dispense measured volume of liquids with a rapid release valve for quick and easy dispensing. These are autoclavable and light to use with disposable pipette tips.', 'Micropipettes', 'Micropipettes', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling/Micropipettes', NULL),
(100020, 0, 'Pipette stand', 100003, 2, 'Pipette stand  is made from clear acrylic or high density polyethylene, and accommodates most major brands of pipettors making it a useful addition to any laboratory. We offer 3 types of Pipette Stand for user convenience.', 'Pipette stand', 'Pipette-stand', 'Liquid Handling | Pipette stand | Lab Equipment', 'Pipette stand  is made from clear acrylic or high density polyethylene, and accommodates most major brands of pipettors making it a useful addition to any laboratory. We offer 3 types of Pipette Stand for user convenience.', 'Pipette stand', 'Pipette stand', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling/Pipette-stand', NULL),
(100021, 0, 'Pipette Pump', 100003, 2, 'Pipette Pumps Features a rotating thumb wheel for drawing up or dispensing liquid. Syringe-type, for easy, one-hand control of filling and delivery from conventional pipets. Offered in three color-coded sizes. Provides relaxed, precise pipetting. Economical and resilient manual pipette.', 'Pipette Pump', 'Pipette-Pump', 'Liquid Handling | Pipette Pump | Lab Equipment', 'Pipette Pumps Features a rotating thumb wheel for drawing up or dispensing liquid. Syringe-type, for easy, one-hand control of filling and delivery from conventional pipets. Offered in three color-coded sizes. Provides relaxed, precise pipetting. Economical and resilient manual pipette.', 'Pipette Pump', 'Pipette Pump', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling/Pipette-Pump', NULL),
(100022, 0, 'Centrifuge Tubes', 100004, 2, 'Our Centrifuge Tubes feature easy to read, white ink graduation with frosted marking areas. Made up of Virgin Polypropylene, providing excellent chemical resistance and mechanical strength. Availability of two sizes with bulk packaging in Bags and Foam Rack.', 'Centrifuge Tubes', 'Centrifuge-Tubes', 'Centrifuge Consumables | Centrifuge Tubes | Lab Equipment', 'Our Centrifuge Tubes feature easy to read, white ink graduation with frosted marking areas. Made up of Virgin Polypropylene, providing excellent chemical resistance and mechanical strength. Availability of two sizes with bulk packaging in Bags and Foam Rack.', 'Centrifuge Tubes', 'Centrifuge Tubes', NULL, 'Labware/Centrifuge-Consumables/Centrifuge-Tubes', NULL),
(100023, 0, 'Centrifuge Tube Rack', 100004, 2, 'Centrifuge Tube Rack display excellent chemical resistance and abstain from corrosion. With a resistant temperature of 121 Â°C, tube identification and organization is easy due to excellent color-coding feature and addition of letters and numbers on the top row of the rack.', 'Centrifuge Tube Rack', 'Centrifuge-Tube-Rack', 'Centrifuge Consumables | Centrifuge Tube Rack | Lab Equipment', 'Centrifuge Tube Rack display excellent chemical resistance and abstain from corrosion. With a resistant temperature of 121 Â°C, tube identification and organization is easy due to excellent color-coding feature and addition of letters and numbers on the top row of the rack.', 'Centrifuge Tube Rack', 'Centrifuge Tube Rack', NULL, 'Labware/Centrifuge-Consumables/Centrifuge-Tube-Rack', NULL),
(100024, 0, 'Microcentrifuge Tube', 100004, 2, 'Micro Centrifuge Tubes provide chemical resistance with durability built for high collision usage and can resist over 28,000 x g when swirled. Itâ€™s rigid, with a flat top cap that is easy to open and yet protected with a tight seal. Made up of clear polypropylene offering transparency for easy and convenient sample identification.', 'Microcentrifuge Tube', 'Microcentrifuge-Tube', 'Centrifuge Consumables | Microcentrifuge Tube | Lab Equipment', 'Micro Centrifuge Tubes provide chemical resistance with durability built for high collision usage and can resist over 28,000 x g when swirled. Itâ€™s rigid, with a flat top cap that is easy to open and yet protected with a tight seal. Made up of clear polypropylene offering transparency for easy and convenient sample identification.', 'Microcentrifuge Tube', 'Microcentrifuge Tube', NULL, 'Labware/Centrifuge-Consumables/Microcentrifuge-Tube', NULL),
(100025, 0, 'Microcentrifuge Tube Rack', 100004, 2, 'Micro centrifuge tube rack are autoclavable racks with a compatible holding capacity of 1.5 mL, 2.0 mL, 5.0 mL and 15.0 mL. Available with color coding facility for easy identification. Equipped with 50 wells and a diameter of 12.2 and 18 mm for varying range of tubes', 'Microcentrifuge Tube Rack', 'Microcentrifuge-Tube-Rack', 'Centrifuge Consumables | Microcentrifuge Tube Rack | Lab Equipment', 'Micro centrifuge tube rack are autoclavable racks with a compatible holding capacity of 1.5 mL, 2.0 mL, 5.0 mL and 15.0 mL. Available with color coding facility for easy identification. Equipped with 50 wells and a diameter of 12.2 and 18 mm for varying range of tubes', 'Microcentrifuge Tube Rack', 'Microcentrifuge Tube Rack', NULL, 'Labware/Centrifuge-Consumables/Microcentrifuge-Tube-Rack', NULL),
(100026, 0, 'Cell Culture Flask', 100005, 2, 'Cell Culture Flasks feature large neck with allowance for relaxed pipette access. Wehave both Cell culture treated and Non cell culture treated flask. Cell culture treatment on these flasks offers a better surface for cell attachment and growth. Non-treated flasks are innovated with an angled neck design for better pipet access.Availability of both vent cap and plug seal cap. Made of high transparency polystyrene for precised microscopic viewing. Exclusively leak tested and sterilized flasks by gamma irradiation.', 'Cell Culture Flask', 'Cell-Culture-Flask', 'Cell Culture Products | Cell Culture Flask | Lab Equipment', 'Cell Culture Flasks feature large neck with allowance for relaxed pipette access. Wehave both Cell culture treated and Non cell culture treated flask. Cell culture treatment on these flasks offers a better surface for cell attachment and growth. Non-treated flasks are innovated with an angled neck design for better pipet access.Availability of both vent cap and plug seal cap. Made of high transparency polystyrene for precised microscopic viewing. Exclusively leak tested and sterilized flasks by gamma irradiation.', 'Cell Culture Flask', 'Cell Culture Flask', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Cell-Culture-Flask', NULL);
