(100027, 0, 'Cell Culture Plate', 100005, 2, 'Cell Culture Plates are featured with a raised rim which nestles into the rings on the single directioned lid for reduced evaporation limiting the risk of cross contamination. Each well is labeled with large alpha-numeric markings for easy identification. Distinctively featured with sterile flat surfaced bottom, RNase, DNase and pyrogen free.', 'Cell Culture Plate', 'Cell-Culture-Plate', 'Cell Culture Products | Cell Culture Plate | Lab Equipment', 'Cell Culture Plates are featured with a raised rim which nestles into the rings on the single directioned lid for reduced evaporation limiting the risk of cross contamination. Each well is labeled with large alpha-numeric markings for easy identification. Distinctively featured with sterile flat surfaced bottom, RNase, DNase and pyrogen free.', 'Cell Culture Plate', 'Cell Culture Plate', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Cell-Culture-Plate', NULL),
(100028, 0, 'Cell Scraper', 100005, 2, 'Cell Scrapers feature an angled swivel blade, minimizing cell damage and assures even contact with the growth area. Designed to provide maximum accessibility to growth surfaces. Available in two lengths, with adjustable blade for optimal application flexibility.', 'Cell Scraper', 'Cell-Scraper', 'Cell Culture Products | Cell Scraper | Lab Equipment', 'Cell Scrapers feature an angled swivel blade, minimizing cell damage and assures even contact with the growth area. Designed to provide maximum accessibility to growth surfaces. Available in two lengths, with adjustable blade for optimal application flexibility.', 'Cell Scraper', 'Cell Scraper', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Cell-Scraper', NULL),
(100029, 0, 'Cell Spreader', 100005, 2, 'Cell Spreader with high-impact polypropylene making it durable for spreading cells onto the surface of an agar plate. Each spreader is supplied sterile and detectable free pyrogen, RNase and DNase.', 'Cell Spreader', 'Cell-Spreader', 'Cell Culture Products | Cell Spreader | Lab Equipment', 'Cell Spreader with high-impact polypropylene making it durable for spreading cells onto the surface of an agar plate. Each spreader is supplied sterile and detectable free pyrogen, RNase and DNase.', 'Cell Spreader', 'Cell Spreader', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Cell-Spreader', NULL),
(100030, 0, 'Cell Strainer', 100005, 2, 'Cell Strainers are compatible with standard 50mL centrifuge tubes, thus can be used for many applications including isolating cells and removing clumps or debris. Extended grip enables aseptic handling. Packaged sterile (gamma irradiated), non-cytotoxic, DNase, RNase and pyrogen free.', 'Cell Strainer', 'Cell-Strainer', 'Cell Culture Products | Cell Strainer | Lab Equipment', 'Cell Strainers are compatible with standard 50mL centrifuge tubes, thus can be used for many applications including isolating cells and removing clumps or debris. Extended grip enables aseptic handling. Packaged sterile (gamma irradiated), non-cytotoxic, DNase, RNase and pyrogen free.', 'Cell Strainer', 'Cell Strainer', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Cell-Strainer', NULL),
(100031, 0, 'Inoculating Loop & Needle', 100005, 2, 'Inoculating Needles and Loop made of Polypropylene for precised requirement of applications. Smooth and bendable allowing uniform and scratch less streaking onto the gel surface. Packed in sterile, tamper-proof bags for contamination free transportation. Can be used under hoods without danger, and are color-coded for ease of size identification.', 'Inoculating Loop & Needle', 'Inoculating-Loop-Needle', 'Cell Culture Products | Inoculating Loop & Needle | Lab Equipment', 'Inoculating Needles and Loop made of Polypropylene for precised requirement of applications. Smooth and bendable allowing uniform and scratch less streaking onto the gel surface. Packed in sterile, tamper-proof bags for contamination free transportation. Can be used under hoods without danger, and are color-coded for ease of size identification.', 'Inoculating Loop & Needle', 'Inoculating Loop & Needle', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Inoculating-Loop-Needle', NULL),
(100032, 0, 'Embedding Cassette', 100005, 2, 'Embedding Cassettes features anterior writing area at an angle of 45Â° to making it an universal cassette. Made from a special high density polymer Polyoxymethylene keeping specimens safely submerged in solution. Resistant to most histological solvents. The slots provided offer maximum flow for good fluid exchange and proper drainage. The lids either come attached to the cassette or are packaged separately.', 'Embedding Cassette', 'Embedding-Cassette', 'Cell Culture Products | Embedding Cassette | Lab Equipment', 'Embedding Cassettes features anterior writing area at an angle of 45Â° to making it an universal cassette. Made from a special high density polymer Polyoxymethylene keeping specimens safely submerged in solution. Resistant to most histological solvents. The slots provided offer maximum flow for good fluid exchange and proper drainage. The lids either come attached to the cassette or are packaged separately.', 'Embedding Cassette', 'Embedding Cassette', NULL, 'Labware/Cell-Culture-Products/Embedding-Cassette', NULL),
(100033, 0, 'Solution Reservoir', 100002, 2, 'Our Solution Basins are made of natural Virgin Polystyrene and sterilized by irradiation. Made for easy withdrawal and features corner pouring lips to facilitate pour-out. They are designed for 8 and 12-channel multichannel pipettors. The 65 mL reservoir with a divider accommodates eight channel pipets on one side and up to four channel pipets on the opposite side.', 'Solution Reservoir', 'Solution-Reservoir', 'General Laboratory Products | Solution Reservoir | Lab Equipment', 'Our Solution Basins are made of natural Virgin Polystyrene and sterilized by irradiation. Made for easy withdrawal and features corner pouring lips to facilitate pour-out. They are designed for 8 and 12-channel multichannel pipettors. The 65 mL reservoir with a divider accommodates eight channel pipets on one side and up to four channel pipets on the opposite side.', 'Solution Reservoir', 'Solution Reservoir', NULL, 'Labware/General-Laboratory-Products/Solution-Reservoir', NULL),
(100034, 0, 'Pipette Controller', 100003, 2, 'Pipet Controller is a light, ergonomic pipette controller designed for use with glass and plastic serological pipets from 0.1 to 100 mL. Suitably placed switches change operating modes and speeds quickly to handle different liquid volumes. When fully charged, the batteries enable up to 8 hours of constant use. The large LCD display clearly indicated battery status and speed.', 'Pipette Controller', 'Pipette-Controller', 'Liquid Handling | Pipette Controller | Lab Equipment', 'Pipet Controller is a light, ergonomic pipette controller designed for use with glass and plastic serological pipets from 0.1 to 100 mL. Suitably placed switches change operating modes and speeds quickly to handle different liquid volumes. When fully charged, the batteries enable up to 8 hours of constant use. The large LCD display clearly indicated battery status and speed.', 'Pipette Controller', 'Pipette Controller', NULL, 'Labware/Liquid-Handling/Pipette-Controller', NULL),
(100035, 0, 'Cryoware', 20002, 1, 'We fabricate internal Cryovials, external Cryovials and Cryovials holders for storage of specimens and vials at ultra-low temperatures. Designed with special chemical resistant and durable material. Color coded for prÃ©cised use of cross reference.', 'Cryoware', 'Cryoware', 'Labware | Cryoware | Lab Equipment', 'We fabricate internal Cryovials, external Cryovials and Cryovials holders for storage of specimens and vials at ultra-low temperatures. Designed with special chemical resistant and durable material. Color coded for prÃ©cised use of cross reference.', 'Cryoware', 'Cryoware', NULL, 'Labware/Cryoware', NULL),
(100036, 0, 'Screw Cap Microtubes', 100035, 2, 'Our Screw Top Micro Tubes feature molded TPE sealing rings deigned to have a good sealablity. Caps are available in various colors for easy identification and color-coding. Caps can either be screw-on or attached to the Micro tubes. Available in conical- or self standing designs.', 'Screw Cap Microtubes', 'Screw-Cap-Microtubes', 'Cryoware | Screw Cap Microtubes | Lab Equipment', 'Our Screw Top Micro Tubes feature molded TPE sealing rings deigned to have a good sealablity. Caps are available in various colors for easy identification and color-coding. Caps can either be screw-on or attached to the Micro tubes. Available in conical- or self standing designs.', 'Screw Cap Microtubes', 'Screw Cap Microtubes', NULL, 'Labware/Cryoware/Screw-Cap-Microtubes', NULL);
